      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;single-responsibility-principle&#34;&gt;S)ingle Responsibility Principle&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;A class should have one, and only one, reason to change.&lt;/em&gt;&#xA;A class should have a single responsibility within the software.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Bad Example:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#ebdbb2;background-color:#282828;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-kotlin&#34; data-lang=&#34;kotlin&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#756d59&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#fe8019&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; User {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#756d59&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#fe8019&#34;&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#fabd2f&#34;&gt;save&lt;/span&gt;() {&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#756d59&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#928374;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;// Logic to save user to the database&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#756d59&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#928374;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;    }&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;